summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5914 for the improvement of West Holden Street, from 35th Avenue Southwest to approximately 132 feet west of California Avenue; by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 78072, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
